{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "ZMYZVV37YZTK7UBXWT7RA5WUFQN6C25R",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "830024002",
    "title": "本当に応えるべきは……",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――この日は<chrname>のため、\r\nレース場の下見に来ていたのだが……。",
            "enText": "—I had come to preview the racetrack \nthat day for <chrname>…",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -2936538048359560259
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 9100244503938409183
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4908011312236348418,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "記者",
            "enName": "Reporter",
            "jpText": "いやぁ、オグリさん聞きましたよ！\r\nぬいぐるみの制作＆発売を記念して\nイベントが開催されるとか！",
            "enText": "Well, Oguri-san, I heard about it! I heard \nthere's going to be an event to celebrate \nthe creation & release of the plushie!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 4474755898458132799
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": -6096523103847394836
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": -2520796247433912391
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3049892854606565966,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "……あ、ありがとう。",
            "enText": "… Oh, thank you.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 58,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -6861130751065863024
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": -8807710991964218688
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -1329181604303088169
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3762959868829719827,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "記者",
            "enName": "Reporter",
            "jpText": "さすがスター。ご家族も喜んでいるでしょう！\r\nで、いつお会いになるんです？\nぜひ、感動のコメントを独占でいただきたい！",
            "enText": "That's the star. Your family must be so \nhappy! So, when are you going to meet them? \nI'd love to have an exclusive commentary on \nyour excitement!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 121,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -4898070461886048379
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": -2764393297815466563
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 132,
                    "pathId": -4479702489300835409
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6877479675323118602,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "いや。両親は故郷にいるので――",
            "enText": "No, I don't. My parents are back home, so…",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 2040916619677776906
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": 7362826351615374257
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": 4589384883072278475
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3918280658022018506,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "記者",
            "enName": "Reporter",
            "jpText": "おっと、ではお電話でも結構です！\r\nそうですね～……まずはぜひご実家の\n電話番号を教えていただけますと……。",
            "enText": "Oops, you can call me then! Yes~… \nif you could please give me your \nparents' phone number first…",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": 2264028329494223088
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": 9109086993129029864
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2087637926025275199,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "で、電話か？\r\nええっと、それなら……0――",
            "enText": "So, you're calling? Well, that's…0—",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": -7160160010162053377
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": 7903506524072643748
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5454406255761094944,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……さすがに取材だとしても、\r\n個人情報を聞き出すのは度が過ぎている。\nこれ以上は学園関係者として見過ごせない。",
            "enText": "… Even if it is indeed an interview, \nasking for personal information is \ntoo much. I'm not sure what to make \nof it, but it's a good idea.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "以降の質問は、学園を通してください",
                    "enText": "Subsequent questions should be \ndirected through the school.",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": 5434626107031809127
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": 5567108544527593733
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -764935525669635300,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "記者",
            "enName": "Reporter",
            "jpText": "え、あなたは？　……はっ、そのバッジ！\r\nあ、あはは。学園の方でしたか！\nこれは失礼しました～……！",
            "enText": "What about you? … haha, that badge! \nAh, haha. You're from the academy! \nI'm sorry about this~…!",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 94,
                    "pathId": -1441787469185064747
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": -3293859817851843959
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8899688525632399171,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "……助けてくれてありがとう。\r\nやはり彼は記者として、\nよくない人だったんだな。",
            "enText": "… Thanks for the help. I guess she wasn't a \ngood reporter after all.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "怪しいと思ったらすぐ断ろう",
                    "enText": "If something seems fishy, \nturn it down right away.",
                    "nextBlock": 11
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": 7235853664475922192
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 137,
                    "pathId": -4237949363338283895
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1350217996032311071,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "それは……そうなんだが。",
            "enText": "That's… true.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 60,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 33,
                    "pathId": -1895319158661928758
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": -5503953273766028332
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4764411586165789903,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "……実は先ほど、あの記者に、\r\n私はスターウマ娘だと言われたんだ。",
            "enText": "… Actually, that reporter told me earlier \nthat I was a star horse girl.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": 1122161419210222764
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": -2664858205309751821
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2699797568858306361,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "『スターならば質問に答える義務がある。\r\nファンもそれを望んでいる』……と。",
            "enText": "'If you're a star, you have to answer \nquestions. The fans want that, too.\"…",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -5851513235114735850
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 6333391729986496681
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5756318332926396468,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "ならば質問を断ってしまったら――",
            "enText": "Then if you turn down the question—",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 53,
                    "pathId": -504525409739042294
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -611203046008518595
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8846734004974107334,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "……私はみんなの期待を\r\n裏切ることになるんじゃないか？",
            "enText": "… I'm going to disappoint \neveryone, aren't I?",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 57,
                    "pathId": -535947109607021917
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": -6638582179274335583
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4878719785068276827,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……話を聞くに彼女はとてもファン想いの\r\nウマ娘のようだ。ならば、なおさら――",
            "enText": "I've heard of… and she seems to be a very \nfanatical Uma girl. And even more so.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "きちんと断らないとダメだ",
                    "enText": "You have to say no properly.",
                    "nextBlock": 17
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "きちんと断らないとダメ",
                    "enText": "You have to say no properly.",
                    "nextBlock": 17
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -4501514232292613640
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -1660678879623997854
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4659342564004130393,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "……しかし……。",
            "enText": "… but…",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 55,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ファンも君を大切にしたいはず",
                    "enText": "Your fans will want to take care of you.",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "ファンも貴方を大切にしたいはず",
                    "enText": "I'm sure your fans want to take care of you.",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 44,
                    "pathId": -7377318415005152908
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -5847188071522499660
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 717851535269208145,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "……！",
            "enText": "…!",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 48,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 35,
                    "pathId": -1453823576708321375
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 756043218711968651
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1403615507259116728,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "……そうか、そうだな。\r\nトメさんやシゲさんもよく言っていた。",
            "enText": "… Oh, yeah, that's right. Tomi \nand Shige used to say that.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 48,
                    "pathId": -8599084748484492639
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 24917695196756047
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5475747023637971732,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "『オグリちゃんは私たちの宝』と。\r\n私も守るべきだったんだな……その宝を。",
            "enText": "You are our treasure. I guess I should have \nprotected… that treasure, too.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 73,
                    "pathId": -4644377930773857392
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": -3036990521887921071
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5422453031050084762,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "うん。わかった。\r\n次からは断ることにしよう。",
            "enText": "Yeah. I understand. I'll say no next time.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 75,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": -7659914870089444133
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 86,
                    "pathId": -1020011759226427508
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6963763374974238695,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "……だが、うまく断れるだろうか。",
            "enText": "… but will I be able to say no successfully?",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "その時は大人を頼って",
                    "enText": "And when you do, rely on an adult.",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "魔法の言葉を教えよう",
                    "enText": "I'll teach you the magic words.",
                    "nextBlock": 30
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 31,
                    "pathId": 2813666911667319205
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -902929858327020750
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3313147277829395821,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "……なるほど。",
            "enText": "… I see.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 54,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -5413051852302167048
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": -5913705584824143987
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2860429397871001247,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "では今後もよろしく頼む。",
            "enText": "So, please keep up the good work.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 60,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "俺？",
                    "enText": "Me?",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "私？",
                    "enText": "Private?",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": -3652859501588067423
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": 6252382378691202592
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6869058867782389414,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "ああ。先ほどのキミの対応は素晴らしかった。\r\nそれに幸いなことにキミは学園の関係者だ。",
            "enText": "Yeah. You did a great job earlier. \nAnd fortunately for you, you're \naffiliated with the school.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": 2009875354390196848
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 3746830092602494893
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": 7594618558930949192
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7385823337739858221,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "……だから頼ってもよいのだろう？",
            "enText": "It's… so we can rely on it, right?",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 27,
                    "pathId": 4736354960454637149
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -1001985942588593789
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6732598442084435231,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……何とも素直な回答が来てしまったが\r\n彼女の言い分はまさしく正しい。しかし――",
            "enText": "… What a straightforward answer I got, but \nshe's exactly right. But—",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "君は素直すぎる所があるな",
                    "enText": "You're a little too straightforward \nfor your own good.",
                    "nextBlock": 28
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "貴方は素直すぎる所があるね",
                    "enText": "You're a little too honest \nfor your own good.",
                    "nextBlock": 28
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 8545968624317338006
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 386066748298686051
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7313944675010667563,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "ああ、らしいな。\r\n母からもよくそう褒められていた。",
            "enText": "Yeah, that's typical. That's what my mother \nused to praise me for.",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -7945523103061613607
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 6592090555890705715
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3812962135163727052,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その後、学園の大人たちにオグリキャップが\r\n率直に質問する姿を見かけたのだった。",
            "enText": "Afterwards, she saw Oguri-cap asking \nthe adults at the school a few straightforward \nquestions.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -7102911402443077096
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 4431691337219240760
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6480968900335344787,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "……魔法の言葉？",
            "enText": "… Magic words?",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 55,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "『学園を通してください』",
                    "enText": "\"Please go through the school.\"",
                    "nextBlock": 31
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 42,
                    "pathId": 6692881392903155878
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -5152409989483208080
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 68346585592059941,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "それは……さっきキミが言っていた……！？",
            "enText": "That's the… you were talking about earlier…!",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 51,
                    "pathId": -8329939659329685846
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 120895685796732633
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1838192960742897503,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "オグリキャップ",
            "enName": "Oguri Cap",
            "jpText": "なるほど。あの記者もそれを聞くと、\r\nすぐに逃げて行ってしまったな。ふむ……。",
            "enText": "I see. That reporter ran away as \nsoon as she heard that. Hmm…",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 6021181110120260602
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 2490958283918226480
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5062907884798924596,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
